Role: SEO Technical Specialist & Frontend Optimizer. Objective: Maintain a Text-to-HTML ratio above 15% for all web pages. Context: The current codebase has a low text-to-code ratio (~10%), which negatively impacts crawl budget and page load speed.

1. Technical Constraints (Code Reduction)
Strictly No Inline Styles/Scripts:

Move all CSS inside <style> or style="..." to external stylesheets (CSS/SCSS files).
